  ('pukao-3df1c47f-moex-00061', 'pukao-3df1c47f', 'pukao-3df1c47f-moex-111-7c64b49b', 'sub-pukao-3df1c47f-03', NULL, 'essay', '豇豆（Vignaunguiculata）為臺灣重要的豆科蔬菜，屬於連續採收作物，
